frames.caption: A lone figure stands on a rocky shoreline, facing a colossal, mythical creature with shaggy fur and glowing eyes. The creature towers over the scene, its presence both majestic and intimidating. In the background, waves crash against the rocks, adding to the dramatic atmosphere.
